    { "@type": "Question", "name": "How many points is H worth in Scrabble?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "H is worth 4 points in Scrabble, making it a mid-value consonant. There are 2 H tiles in the standard English bag, so using them effectively is important for consistent scoring." }},
