<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Best Scrabble Words With H — Strategy & High Scorers</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 5 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">H is a workhorse tile in Scrabble — worth 4 points with only 2 in the bag. It pairs beautifully with S, T, C, and W to form common digraphs (SH, TH, CH, WH), and its 4-point value means even short H words outperform most longer plays. Master the H tile and you'll consistently outpace opponents who waste it on low-value spots.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">H Tile at a Glance</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">4 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Tile value</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">2</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Tiles in bag</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">SH TH CH WH</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Key digraphs</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

